<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="#Vibrissal_corticostriatal_projections"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Vibrissal corticostriatal projections</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="#Principles_of_corticostriatal_convergence"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Principles of corticostriatal convergence</span></a></li>
